glossdef.para:
A user role that has the highest level of control in the &susemgr;
Web interface. A &susemgr; administrator can assign the &susemgr;
administrator role to other users. However, without also having the role
of an organization administrator, a &susemgr; administrator cannot
edit user details for organization users. An organization must have at
least one &susemgr; administrator assigned.
